<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-56CD2771-85B7-42BB-B8E5-26E5D961C024" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-56CD2771-85B7-42BB-B8E5-26E5D961C024" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Gloss deviations SAV-media</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-50B00AD6-0A38-41AB-B3CF-DCE2951AFA8A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/><table id="GUID-53E5F599-B620-44AD-919D-C7253ABD770C" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Schematic overview 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Real example 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-01B35AFB-148C-4929-8D1C-FC25AB141E2C" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-0562718C-A4DE-4733-8C24-7ED769D68062-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0562718C-A4DE-4733-8C24-7ED769D68062-low.png"/></fig></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7E3F3FFA-535E-4C21-9E41-33569287ACC3" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-A949B584-5C17-4331-A0E1-04BCBB63FDBD-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A949B584-5C17-4331-A0E1-04BCBB63FDBD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-EC1EAE23-40EC-4B10-A2C9-83873F76DC70" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Symptoms</b> 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Only visible on SAV-media 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Local differences in gloss 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Local differences in OD 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">In most case a somewhat “Cloudy”/”stained” appearance 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The “stains” can be seen all over the image
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Functional logging (if available)</b>
</p><p class="- topic/p "> No logging available which can pinpoint to this case.
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ADAM-triggers</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No ADAM triggers are available 
</p></section><section id="GUID-65EDF229-8CE4-467B-BF79-DE632E457299" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the SAV-media is past it’s expiry date. If it’s past the expiry date, use another batch or roll. If it’s not expired cut off the 1st meter of the roll, so the image is printed on a fresh (‘non oxided’) top-layer.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case the issue is not solved the media is not suitable for the Colorado printers
</p></section><section id="GUID-2513E5DF-C282-453D-9841-6E539DB0EB51" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Evaluate/Prevention</title><p class="- topic/p ">Use the SAV-media within the expiry dates and store the media as indicated on the box and specified environmental conditions.
</p></section><section id="GUID-987F83F9-80F0-41BC-B82B-BB16DA268203" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Background info</title><p class="- topic/p ">SAV media is known for its interaction with Air/Oxygen. After some time the surfactants will diffuse to the top-layer of the media. This will influence the spreading behavior of the top-layer. This is one of the reasons there is an expiry date on this kind of media.
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-945E6C60-1212-47DF-9487-92374227D4B4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Solutions</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
